sequenceDiagram
  %% Diagram 39: Payment Webhook Verification and Idempotent Processing

  autonumber
  participant GW as Payment Gateway
  participant API as /api/payments/webhook
  participant Verify as Signature + Provider Verification
  participant Store as Payment Store
  participant Event as Event Bus

  GW->>API: Webhook payload
  API->>Verify: Verify signature/HMAC
  alt Signature invalid
    Verify-->>API: Mismatch
    API-->>GW: Reject + security log
  else Signature valid
    API->>Verify: Server-side transaction verification
    alt Provider says invalid
      Verify-->>API: Not completed
      API-->>GW: No state change
    else Provider confirmed
      API->>Store: Idempotency check by payment reference
      alt Duplicate callback
        Store-->>API: Already processed
        API-->>GW: 200 idempotent no-op
      else First valid callback
        API->>Store: Mark payment confirmed
        API->>Event: Emit payment-confirmed event
        API-->>GW: 200 processed
      end
    end
  end
